<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>{{ project_title }} — {{ subtitle }}</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f5f6f8;
    --panel: #ffffff;
    --ink: #1f2933;
    --muted: #5c6773;
    --line: #e3e6ea;
    --accent: #1f4f8b;
    --accent-soft: #e8f0f9;
    --high: #b3261e;
    --high-soft: #fdecea;
    --medium: #b06b00;
    --medium-soft: #fff4d6;
    --low: #2f6f4d;
    --low-soft: #e6f4ec;
    --positive: #2f6f4d;
    --negative: #b3261e;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB",
      "Helvetica Neue", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .page {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 28px 64px;
  }
  header.hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f4f8b 0%, #2f6f8f 100%);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(31, 79, 139, 0.18);
  }
  header.hero .eyebrow {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    font-size: 12px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  header.hero h1 {
    margin: 6px 0 4px;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  header.hero .subtitle {
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.92;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  header.hero .meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.92;
  }
  header.hero .meta span strong { font-weight: 600; }
  .disclaimer {
    margin-top: 18px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-left: 3px solid #ffd66b;
  }
  .disclaimer .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #ffd66b;
    color: #5b3b00;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-right: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  section.panel {
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  section.panel > h2 {
    margin: 0 0 4px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  section.panel > .section-hint {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .stat-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .stat-card .label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .stat-card .value {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .stat-card.tone-high { background: var(--high-soft); border-color: #f3c2bd; }
  .stat-card.tone-high .value { color: var(--high); }
  .stat-card.tone-medium { background: var(--medium-soft); border-color: #f0d79a; }
  .stat-card.tone-medium .value { color: var(--medium); }
  .stat-card.tone-low { background: var(--low-soft); border-color: #b9dac5; }
  .stat-card.tone-low .value { color: var(--low); }
  .meta-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .meta-row strong { color: var(--ink); }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  table th, table td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  table th {
    background: #f7f9fb;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .severity-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .severity-pill.high { background: var(--high-soft); color: var(--high); }
  .severity-pill.medium { background: var(--medium-soft); color: var(--medium); }
  .severity-pill.low { background: var(--low-soft); color: var(--low); }
  .delta-positive { color: var(--positive); font-weight: 600; }
  .delta-negative { color: var(--negative); font-weight: 600; }
  .delta-neutral { color: var(--muted); }
  .target-block {
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    border: 1px solid #c4d6ed;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .target-block h3 {
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .target-block .target-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .target-block .target-meta strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .driver-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-rank {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-role {
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-contribution {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .driver-card .driver-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-meta strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .driver-card p { margin: 8px 0 0; }
  .process-group {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .process-group h3 {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .roadmap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .roadmap .card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .roadmap .card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .roadmap ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; }
  .roadmap li { margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
  .limitations-list { margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; }
  .limitations-list li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .limitations-list .source {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-right: 6px;
  }
  .next-steps-list { margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; }
  .next-steps-list li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .next-steps-list .source-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 1px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-right: 6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  footer.footer {
    margin-top: 32px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .empty {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main class="page">

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">{{ dashboard_version }}</div>
    <h1>{{ project_title }}</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">{{ subtitle }}</div>
    <div class="meta">
      <span><strong>报告生成时间</strong>：{{ generated_at_display }}</span>
      {% if overview.baseline_window %}
      <span><strong>基线窗口</strong>：{{ overview.baseline_window }}</span>
      {% endif %}
      {% if overview.recent_window %}
      <span><strong>最近窗口</strong>：{{ overview.recent_window }}</span>
      {% endif %}
      {% if report_version %}
      <span><strong>M3 报告版本</strong>：{{ report_version }}</span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <div class="disclaimer">
      <span class="tag">Demo Disclaimer</span>
      {{ demo_disclaimer }}
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="panel" id="overview">
    <h2>1. 异常总览</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">基于 M3-A 异常检测引擎输出，统计本轮触发的异常数量与严重度分布。</div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for card in overview.cards %}
      <div class="stat-card tone-{{ card.tone }}">
        <div class="label">{{ card.label }}</div>
        <div class="value">{{ card.value }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="meta-row">
      <span><strong>归因目标指标</strong>：{{ attribution_target.metric_name_cn }}（{{ attribution_target.metric_code }}）</span>
      {% if attribution_target.anomaly_id %}
      <span><strong>归因目标 anomaly_id</strong>：{{ attribution_target.anomaly_id }}</span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% if overview.warnings %}
    <div class="meta-row">
      <span><strong>warnings</strong>：{{ overview.warnings | join('；') }}</span>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="high-priority">
    <h2>2. 高优先级异常列表</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">按 severity 排序展示需要优先处置的异常事件。</div>
    {% if high_priority_anomalies %}
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>指标</th>
          <th>severity</th>
          <th>维度</th>
          <th>baseline</th>
          <th>recent</th>
          <th>relative change</th>
          <th>下一步建议</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for anomaly in high_priority_anomalies %}
        <tr>
          <td>
            <strong>{{ anomaly.metric_name_cn or anomaly.metric_code }}</strong><br/>
            <span style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px;">{{ anomaly.metric_code }}</span>
          </td>
          <td>
            <span class="severity-pill {{ anomaly.severity }}">{{ anomaly.severity }}</span>
          </td>
          <td>{{ anomaly.dimension_name }} = {{ anomaly.dimension_value }}</td>
          <td>{{ anomaly.baseline_value | metric_value }}</td>
          <td>{{ anomaly.recent_value | metric_value }}</td>
          <td>
            {% set rc = anomaly.relative_change %}
            {% if rc is number %}
              {% if rc > 0 %}
              <span class="delta-positive">{{ rc | signed_pct }}</span>
              {% elif rc < 0 %}
              <span class="delta-negative">{{ rc | signed_pct }}</span>
              {% else %}
              <span class="delta-neutral">{{ rc | signed_pct }}</span>
              {% endif %}
            {% else %}
              N/A
            {% endif %}
          </td>
          <td>{{ anomaly.recommended_next_step or '—' }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    {% else %}
    <p class="empty">本轮无 high severity 异常。</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="attribution">
    <h2>3. M1 D7 回收率下降归因</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">基于 M3-B 归因引擎对目标指标 {{ attribution_target.metric_code }} 的 Top drivers 进行解读。</div>

    {% if attribution_target.anomaly %}
    {% set tgt = attribution_target.anomaly %}
    <div class="target-block">
      <h3>归因目标异常：{{ tgt.metric_name_cn or tgt.metric_code }}</h3>
      <div class="target-meta">
        <span><strong>severity</strong>：<span class="severity-pill {{ tgt.severity }}">{{ tgt.severity }}</span></span>
        <span><strong>维度</strong>：{{ tgt.dimension_name }} = {{ tgt.dimension_value }}</span>
        <span><strong>baseline</strong>：{{ tgt.baseline_value | metric_value }}</span>
        <span><strong>recent</strong>：{{ tgt.recent_value | metric_value }}</span>
        <span><strong>relative change</strong>：
          {% if tgt.relative_change is number %}
            <span class="{% if tgt.relative_change > 0 %}delta-positive{% elif tgt.relative_change < 0 %}delta-negative{% else %}delta-neutral{% endif %}">{{ tgt.relative_change | signed_pct }}</span>
          {% else %}
            N/A
          {% endif %}
        </span>
      </div>
      {% if tgt.explanation %}
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0;">{{ tgt.explanation }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <h3 style="margin: 12px 0 8px; font-size: 15px;">Top 5 drivers</h3>
    {% if top_drivers %}
      {% for driver in top_drivers %}
      <div class="driver-card">
        <div class="driver-head">
          <div>
            <span class="driver-rank">#{{ driver.rank }}</span>
            <span class="driver-title">{{ driver.dimension_name }} = {{ driver.dimension_value }}</span>
            <span class="driver-role">{{ driver.driver_role }}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="driver-contribution">贡献度 {{ driver.contribution_score | pct }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="driver-meta">
          <span><strong>baseline</strong>：{{ driver.baseline_value | metric_value }}</span>
          <span><strong>recent</strong>：{{ driver.recent_value | metric_value }}</span>
          {% if driver.confidence %}
          <span><strong>confidence</strong>：{{ driver.confidence }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% if driver.business_interpretation %}
        <p><strong>业务解释</strong>：{{ driver.business_interpretation }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if driver.recommended_action %}
        <p><strong>推荐动作</strong>：{{ driver.recommended_action }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
    <p class="empty">未生成 Top drivers。</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="process-evidence">
    <h2>4. Process evidence / driver linkage</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">将 Top drivers 与过程指标（PTP 履约 / AI 外呼覆盖 / 减免使用率 / 投诉率）以及产能压力信号对齐。</div>

    {% for group in process_evidence_groups %}
    <div class="process-group">
      <h3>{{ group.group_label }}</h3>
      {% if group.entries %}
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>driver</th>
            <th>过程指标</th>
            <th>baseline</th>
            <th>recent</th>
            <th>delta</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {% for entry in group.entries %}
          <tr>
            <td>{{ entry.driver }}</td>
            <td>{{ entry.metric_name_cn or entry.metric_code }}</td>
            <td>{{ entry.baseline_value | metric_value }}</td>
            <td>{{ entry.recent_value | metric_value }}</td>
            <td>
              {% if entry.delta is number %}
                <span class="{% if entry.delta > 0 %}delta-positive{% elif entry.delta < 0 %}delta-negative{% else %}delta-neutral{% endif %}">{{ entry.delta | signed_value }}</span>
              {% else %}
                N/A
              {% endif %}
            </td>
          </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
      {% else %}
      <p class="empty">本轮 driver linkage 中未捕获该过程指标。</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}

    <div class="process-group">
      <h3>产能压力信号</h3>
      {% if capacity_signals %}
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>指标</th>
            <th>维度</th>
            <th>baseline</th>
            <th>recent</th>
            <th>relative change</th>
            <th>说明</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {% for item in capacity_signals %}
          <tr>
            <td><strong>{{ item.metric_name_cn or item.metric_code }}</strong></td>
            <td>{{ item.dimension_name }} = {{ item.dimension_value }}</td>
            <td>{{ item.baseline_value | metric_value }}</td>
            <td>{{ item.recent_value | metric_value }}</td>
            <td>
              {% if item.relative_change is number %}
                <span class="{% if item.relative_change > 0 %}delta-positive{% elif item.relative_change < 0 %}delta-negative{% else %}delta-neutral{% endif %}">{{ item.relative_change | signed_pct }}</span>
              {% else %}
                N/A
              {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>{{ item.explanation or '—' }}</td>
          </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
      {% else %}
      <p class="empty">本轮未捕获产能维度异常。</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="limitations">
    <h2>5. 数据局限与合规说明</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">Demo 环境使用的合成数据与隐私边界约束。</div>
    <ul class="limitations-list">
      {% for item in data_limitations %}
      <li>
        <span class="source">{{ item.source }}</span>{{ item.description }}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
      <li><span class="source">privacy</span>未接入真实客户数据，未触达真实客户，未发送短信 / 外呼，未涉及 P4 明文 PII 字段。</li>
      <li><span class="source">human_in_loop</span>所有结论均需人工复核，AI 不直接外发、不直接外呼、不绕过审批。</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="next-steps">
    <h2>6. 下一步建议</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">本轮异常与归因驱动的可执行建议（来自 M3-C 报告）。</div>
    {% if next_steps %}
    <ul class="next-steps-list">
      {% for item in next_steps %}
      <li>
        <span class="source-tag">{{ item.source }}</span>{{ item.next_step }}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% else %}
    <p class="empty">本轮未输出下一步建议。</p>
    {% endif %}

    <h3 style="margin: 18px 0 10px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted);">后续里程碑路线图</h3>
    <div class="roadmap">
      {% for phase in roadmap %}
      <div class="card">
        <h3>{{ phase.phase }}</h3>
        <ul>
          {% for item in phase.bullets %}
          <li>{{ item }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    RiskOps Copilot · {{ subtitle }} · 本页面基于合成数据，仅供 Demo 与作品集展示。
  </footer>
</main>
</body>
</html>
